<abstract><t>This document presents network slicing differentiation from the non- partition network or from simply partition of connectivity resources. It lists 15 standardization gaps related to 6 key requirements for network slicing.  It also presents an analysis of existing related work and other potential solutions on network slicing.  This gap analysis document aims to provide a basis for future works in network slicing.</t></abstract>

